text: Chapelle (Glâne) (Dictionnaire-Dikchenéro: Français-Patois/Patê-Franché. Société cantonale des patoisans fribourgeois. Fribourg: 2013. p. 101) is a municipality of the district of Glâne in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. Since 2005, Chapelle (Broye) in the same canton is part of the municipality of Cheiry. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Municipalities in Glâne
title: Chapelle, Glâne
